ers total power of 3000GH / s, <span id=\"result_box\"><span>You upgrade to an international ambassador, get a super cloud machine 1, enjoy GEC trading commission 5% of the global dividend.</span></span><span id=\"t-served-community-button\" class=\"trans-verified-button goog-toolbar-button\"><span class=\"jfk-button-img\"></span></span></span> \r\n</p>',0,0,0,NULL,NULL,0),(35,'2017-11-21 13:58:16',NULL,'',0,0,'GEC系统运行公告','GEC system operation Bulletin','','<p>\r\n	GEC系统于<span>2017</span><span>年</span><span>10</span><span>月</span><span>17<strong><span style=\"color:#006600;\"></span></strong></span><span>日上线运行<span style=\"color:#000000;\">，</span></span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">全球同步送出1000万</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">台微型云矿机（每台价值</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">11</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">个</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">GEC</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">），2017年10月20日交易中心开放。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;\">2017年10月17日至2017年11月28日所有注册会员免费赠送2台微型云矿机。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;\">2017年12月1日起<span>所有注册会员免费赠送1台微型云矿机。</span></span> \r\n</p>','<span id=\"result_box\">The GEC system will be operational on February 17, 2017, and&nbsp;<span id=\"result_box\">global simultaneous delivery of 10 million micro-cloud machine (each value of 11 GEC)</span>, and the trading center will open on February 20, 2017.<br />\r\nFebruary 17, 2017 to February 28, 2017, all registered members free of charge 2 sets of micro-cloud machine.<br />\r\nMarch 1, 2017 all registered members free of charge a <span>micro-cloud machine&nbsp;</span>.</span>',0,0,0,NULL,NULL,0),(36,'2017-11-21 13:56:59',NULL,'',0,0,'注册登陆流程','Register login process','','<p>\r\n	进入【公会招募】将您的注册链接或二维码图片发送给需要注册的人\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"http://www.scoop.wang/Public/kindeditor/attached/image/20170221/20170221185227_16336.png\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	打开注册链接或扫描二维码图片进入注册页面\r\n</p>\r\n<p style